es":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据可视化是一个相对的过程，你想要用户看到什么取决于他能看到什么。设计者通过对数据进行编码设计，阅读者再对数据进行解码，去理解可视化背后的数据。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"设计者，"}]},{"type":"text","value":"从数据到图表——数据元素到视觉编码的映射过程"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阅读者，"}]},{"type":"text","value":"从图表到数据——视觉解码还原为数据结构的过程"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*twtrS6DuNsAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"分析模型","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B","ariaLabel":"分析模型 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"分析模型"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们设计数据可视化时，应当站在用户的角度换位思考。用户面对可视化时，通常会套用一个固化的分析思路，它们环环相扣形成闭环，是固定的分析模式，我们称之“分析模型”。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*pwHGQJNBAd4AAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5W 模型最早由 IBM 提出，作为通用分析模型指引分析师进行工作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“发生了什么”、“为什么会发生”、“接下来会发生什么”、“我能做什么”、“我的计划是什么” 这几个问题越往前越浅显偏现象、越往后越偏本质及解决方案，中间有任何卡壳都会影响用户的分析思路甚至导致分析流程中断。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发生了什么？有没有“冲突”？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么会发生？“冲突”的原因是什么？为什么会发生？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接下来会发生什么？有没有特征线索表明“冲突”会持续下去？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我能做什么？怎么避免“冲突”继续 发生或者让“冲突”反转？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的计划是什么？针对“冲突”我能做什么？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以在可视化设计时，应当甄别用户可能会遇到的问题、以看问题的视角来确定数据的展示顺序及视图关系，设计上突显需阐述的道理或规律，让其可以帮助用户透过现象看本质甚至预测未来。"}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specific